More than two months after its establishment by the Iranian authorities, the British oil tanker "Stena Impero" left the port of Bandar Abbas this Friday. Ship observation data from Refinitiv showed that the tanker was moving and leaving the Iranian port. Port Rashid was declared as the destination port in the United Arab Emirates.
