In the Senate, the Republicans seem to be trying to force $12 billion for the construction of the Wall, one of President Trump’s major priorities. The Democrats are disrupting the plans for the construction of the Wall and its financing, which is actually intended for other military buildings and projects. The dispute over the construction of the Wall had escalated in December 2018 and had led to a 35-day shutdown.
At the building of the wall the ghosts separate
